      • createQuizDialog

        public void createQuizDialog(View caller)
        This method creates a AlertDialog when you click on "Create Quiz" in the main menu. In the AlertDialog you will be asked to name your Quiz, once you press enter you will be forwarded to the QuizCreatorActivity. If you press Cancel you will be kicked out to the main menu again.
